    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fish Information</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's a simple clicker game where you feed the fish.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Receive a different type of fish every 3 hours to create your own collection.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[Fish Probability]</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fish : 69.24%</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[Common] Fish : 29.70%</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[Rare] Fish :  0.99%</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[Legendary] Fish : 0.00033%</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In Game Content</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088770/extras/02acacbdf1daab90c8390d1bab0cc832.avif?t=1727335935\" width=270 height=302 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you want to get more fish,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I recommend using this content.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Consume 5 regular &quot;Fish&quot; to get a fish with the &quot;Special&quot; tag.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*&quot;Special&quot; tag can only be obtained from that content.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[Merge Content Probability]</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[Common] Fish : 89.97%</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[Rare] Fish : 9.997%</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[Epic] Fish : 0.989%</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[Special] Fish : 0.03%</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect fish! Then merge them to get more fish and build your collection! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Just turn on the game and you too can become a fish collector!</p>",
